=>'DirectAdmin 已识别。可能证书可以自动安装。','Plesk recognized. Possibly the certificate can be installed automatically.'=>'Plesk 认出了。可能证书可以自动安装。','CPanel recognized. Possibly the certificate can be installed automatically.'=>'CPanel 识别。可能证书可以自动安装。','The Hosting Panel software was not recognized. Depending on your hosting provider, the generated certificate may need to be installed manually.'=>'无法识别主机面板软件。根据您的托管服务提供商，可能需要手动安装生成的证书。','SSL certificate should be generated and installed.'=>'应生成并安装 SSL 证书。','You already have a valid SSL certificate.'=>'您已经拥有有效的 SSL 证书。','Continue to renew.'=>'继续更新。','Your certificate will expire on %s.'=>'您的证书将于 %s 到期。','(unknown)'=>'（未知）','Your domain meets the requirements for Let\'s Encrypt.'=>'您的域符合 Let&#39;s Encrypt 的要求。','It is not possible to install Let\'s Encrypt on a localhost environment.'=>'无法在 localhost 环境中安装 Let&#39;s Encrypt。','It is not possible to install Let\'s Encrypt on a subfolder configuration.'=>'无法在子文件夹配置上安装 Let&#39;s Encrypt。','It is not possible to install Let\'s Encrypt on a subsite. Please go to the main site of your website.'=>'无法在子站点上安装 Let&#39;s Encrypt。请访问您网站的主站点。','Re-check'=>'重新检查','SSL certificate will expire on %s.'=>'SSL 证书将于 %s 到期。','Your SSL certificate will expire soon.'=>'您的 SSL 证书即将过期。','No SSL detected. Use the retry button to check again.'=>'未检测到 SSL。使用重试按钮再次检查。','Install SSL certificate'=>'安装 SSL 证书','Retry'=>'重试','An SSL certificate has been detected'=>'已检测到 SSL 证书','SSL Status Test'=>'SSL状态测试','Security Headers Test'=>'测试安全标头','No SSL detected'=>'未检测到SSL','Enable 301 redirect'=>'启用301重定向','To ensure all traffic passes through SSL, please enable a 301 redirect.'=>'为确保所有流量通过SSL，请启用301重定向。','No 301 redirect to SSL enabled.'=>'没有301重定向到SSL启用。','SSL is not enabled.'=>'SSL未启用。','Completed'=>'完成','Install'=>'安装','Installed'=>'已安装','Open'=>'打开','Warning'=>'警告','WordPress 301 redirect enabled. We recommend to enable a 301 .htaccess redirect.'=>'WordPress 301 重定向已启用。我们建议启用 301 .htaccess 重定向。','Your site uses Divi. This can require some additional steps before getting the secure lock.'=>'您的网站使用了Divi。这可能需要额外的设置，才能获得安全防护。','Your site uses Elementor. This can require some additional steps before getting the secure lock.'=>'您的网站正在使用Elementor。这可能需要额外的设置，才能获得安全防护。','SSL is enabled networkwide.'=>'网络范围内启用了SSL。','Activate SSL'=>'激活SSL','General'=>'一般','Mixed content fixer not enabled. Enable the option to fix mixed content on your site.'=>'混合内容修复未启用。启用该选项以修复您网站上的混合内容。','No recommended redirect rules detected.'=>'未检测到推荐的重定向规则。','Read more'=>'阅读更多','SSL is not enabled yet.'=>'SSL尚未启用。','SSL is not yet enabled on this site.'=>'SSL尚未在该网站启用。','Support'=>'支持','The mixed content fixer is active, but was not detected on the frontpage.'=>'混合内容修复已启用，但是无法在前端页面检测到。','Hi, Really Simple Security has kept your site secure for some time now, awesome! If you have a moment, please consider leaving a review on WordPress.org to spread the word. We greatly appreciate it! If you have any questions or feedback, leave us a %1$smessage%2$s.'=>'嗨，Really Simple SSL已经使您的网站安全了一段时间了，太棒了！ 如果有时间，请考虑在WordPress.org上发表评论以广而告之。 非常感谢！ 如果您有任何疑问或反馈，请和我们%s联络%s。','Don\'t show again'=>'不再显示','The mixed content fixer could not be detected due to a cURL error: %s. cURL errors are often caused by an outdated version of PHP or cURL and don\'t affect the front-end of your site. Contact your hosting provider for a fix.'=>'由于一个 cURL 错误：%s，混合内容修复无法检测。cURL 错误常常是由于旧版的 PHP 或 cURL导致，不会影响到您网站的前端。请联系您的空间服务商寻求修复。','Error occurred when retrieving the webpage.'=>'获取网页时发生错误。','Enable'=>'启用','The 301 .htaccess redirect is the fastest and most reliable redirect option.'=>'301 .htaccess 重定向通常是最快且最可靠的重定向方法。','301 .htaccess redirect is not enabled.'=>'301 .htaccess重定向未启用。','301 SSL redirect enabled'=>'已启用301 SSL重定向','You have set a 301 redirect to SSL. This is important for SEO purposes'=>'您已为SSL设置了一个301重定向。这对于SEO而言很重要','The \'force-deactivate.php\' file has to be renamed to .txt. Otherwise your ssl can be deactivated by anyone on the internet.'=>'\'force-deactivate.php\'文件必须重命名为.txt。 否则，互联网上的任何人都可以停用您的ssl。','Maybe later'=>'也许以后','Leave a review'=>'发表评论','Hi, Really Simple Security has kept your site secure for a month now, awesome! If you have a moment, please consider leaving a review on WordPress.org to spread the word. We greatly appreciate it! If you have any questions or feedback, leave us a %1$smessage%2$s.'=>'嗨，你现在已经使用Really Simple SSL一个月了，棒极了！如果您有时间，请考虑在WordPress.org上留下评论来宣传。我们非常感谢！如果您有任何问题或反馈，请给我们留言%s信息%s。','Activate SSL per site or install a wildcard certificate to fix this.'=>'逐一每站开启 SSL或安装一反遮罩凭证来修护。','This leads to issues when activating SSL networkwide since subdomains will be forced over SSL as well while they don\'t have a valid certificate.'=>'这会在启动 SSL 网际网路时导致些问题，因为子网域也会被强制通过 SSL，而且它并没有有效的 SSL 凭证。','You run a Multisite installation with subdomains, but your site doesn\'t have a wildcard certificate.'=>'透过子网域你执行多重式网站的安装，但是你的网站没有反遮罩凭证。','Cancel'=>'取消','More info'=>'更多资料','Really Simple Security and Really Simple Security add-ons do not process any personal identifiable information, so the GDPR does not apply to these plugins or usage of these plugins on your website. You can find our privacy policy <a href="%s" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">here</a>.'=>'Really Simple SSL 和Really Simple SSL 附加组件不会处理任何个人身份信息，因此GDPR不适用于这些插件或在您的网站上使用这些插件。您可以在这里找到我们的<a href="%s" target="_blank">隐私政策</a>。','Learn more'=>'读取更多','Enable 301 .htaccess redirect'=>'启动301.htaccess导向','No 301 redirect is set. Enable the WordPress 301 redirect in the settings to get a 301 permanent redirect.'=>'301导向没有被设定。请在设定中取得一301永久导向以启动WordPress 301导向。','301 redirect to https set.'=>'301重定向到https设置。','View settings page'=>'查看设置页面','Premium Support'=>'优质支援服務','Instructions'=>'指示程序','SSL is enabled on your site.'=>'SSL 已在您网站启用。','Your wp-config.php has to be edited, but is not writable.'=>'你的wp-config.php 必须要编辑，可是并非可写。','%s is a singleton class and you cannot create a second instance.'=>'%s 是一个单例级而且你无法建立第二例。','Set your wp-config.php to writable and reload this page.'=>'您的wp-config.php设置为可写的并重新加载此页面。','https://really-simple-ssl.com'=>'https://really-simple-ssl.com','Stop editing the .htaccess file'=>'停止编辑 .htaccess 档案','Configuration'=>'配置','Mixed content fixer'=>'混合内容修复程序','Settings'=>'设置','Because the $_SERVER["HTTPS"] variable is not set, your website may experience redirect loops.'=>'因为这$_SERVER["HTTPS"] 变数尚未设好，你的网站可能会经历重导向回圈。','Check again'=>'再检查一遍','You run a Multisite installation with subfolders, which prevents this plugin from fixing your missing server variable in the wp-config.php.'=>'你用子资料夹去执行多站点的安装，会阻止这插件修复你在 wp-config.php 里遗失的伺服器变数。','Activate networkwide to fix this.'=>'在全网络上启用来修复此问题。']];